<div class="conversation-body">
  <div class="conversation-preamble">
    <p class="reveal">Every meaningful thing that has happened in this work began with someone reaching out — not because they knew what they needed, but because something in them knew to reach.</p>
    <p class="reveal">There is no wrong reason to be here. If something from this site stirred something in you, that is enough.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="conversation-paths reveal">
    <div class="convo-path">
      <div class="convo-path-label">I am curious about</div>
      <h3>The Women's Moon Circle</h3>
      <p>Something about gathering in this way, on the rhythm of the moon, with women who are serious about their own unfolding — feels right, even if I cannot fully name why.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="convo-path">
      <div class="convo-path-label">I am looking for</div>
      <h3>Individual Somatic Work</h3>
      <p>Something is held in my body that I have not been able to reach through talking alone. I am ready to try a different kind of conversation — with the body itself.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="convo-path">
      <div class="convo-path-label">I want to explore</div>
      <h3>Dyad Practice</h3>
      <p>The idea of genuine self-inquiry — of being present with another person in a structured way — draws me. I want to understand what this practice actually opens.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="convo-path">
      <div class="convo-path-label">I am a</div>
      <h3>Healthcare Provider</h3>
      <p>I sense there is a somatic dimension to my clinical work that I have not yet been trained to see. I want to find out what that would change.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="conversation-form reveal">
    <p class="form-intro">"Whatever brought you here, say it in your own words. There is no form to fill correctly — only the truth of what is moving in you."</p>
    <div class="form-grid">
      <div class="form-row">
        <div class="form-field"><input id="convName" type="text" placeholder="Your Name"></div>
        <div class="form-field"><input id="convEmail" type="email" placeholder="Your Email"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <select id="convTopic">
          <option value="" disabled selected>What draws you here</option>
          <option>Women's Moon Circle</option>
          <option>Individual Somatic Experiencing</option>
          <option>Dyad Meditation</option>
          <option>Workshops &amp; Intensives</option>
          <option>Practitioner Training</option>
          <option>I'm not sure yet — I just wanted to reach out</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div class="form-field">
        <textarea id="convMessage" placeholder="Say what is true for you right now..."></textarea>
      </div>
      <button class="form-submit" id="formSubmit">Send</button>
    </div>
    <p class="form-note">All inquiries are held with care. You will hear back within a few days.</p>
  </div>
</div>

